DESCRIPTION:FALL BACK (−1 hour)\n\nCities: Azores\, Las Palmas\, Lisbon\, London\, Dublin\, Paris\, Madrid\, Barcelona\, Amsterdam\, Brussels\, Zurich\, Geneva\, Berlin\, Hamburg\, Rome\, Milan\, Vienna\, Prague\, Warsaw\, Krakow\, Budapest\, Ljubljana\, Zagreb\, Sarajevo\, Skopje\, Belgrade\, Tirana\, Stockholm\, Oslo\, Copenhagen\, Athens\, Sofia\, Bucharest\, Vilnius\, Riga\, Tallinn\, Helsinki\, Chisinau\, Kyiv\, Nicosia\, Beirut\, Tel Aviv\, Jerusalem\n\nTimezone changes:\n• Atlantic/Azores: UTC+0 → UTC−1\n• Atlantic/Canary (Las Palmas): UTC+1 → UTC+0\n• Europe/Lisbon: UTC+1 → UTC+0\n• Europe/London: UTC+1 → UTC+0\n• Europe/Dublin: UTC+1 → UTC+0\n• Europe/Paris: UTC+2 → UTC+1\n• Europe/Madrid (Madrid\, Barcelona): UTC+2 → UTC+1\n• Europe/Amsterdam: UTC+2 → UTC+1\n• Europe/Brussels: UTC+2 → UTC+1\n• Europe/Zurich (Zurich\, Geneva): UTC+2 → UTC+1\n• Europe/Berlin (Berlin\, Hamburg): UTC+2 → UTC+1\n• Europe/Rome (Rome\, Milan): UTC+2 → UTC+1\n• Europe/Vienna: UTC+2 → UTC+1\n• Europe/Prague: UTC+2 → UTC+1\n• Europe/Warsaw (Warsaw\, Krakow): UTC+2 → UTC+1\n• Europe/Budapest: UTC+2 → UTC+1\n• Europe/Ljubljana: UTC+2 → UTC+1\n• Europe/Zagreb: UTC+2 → UTC+1\n• Europe/Sarajevo: UTC+2 → UTC+1\n• Europe/Skopje: UTC+2 → UTC+1\n• Europe/Belgrade: UTC+2 → UTC+1\n• Europe/Tirane (Tirana): UTC+2 → UTC+1\n• Europe/Stockholm: UTC+2 → UTC+1\n• Europe/Oslo: UTC+2 → UTC+1\n• Europe/Copenhagen: UTC+2 → UTC+1\n• Europe/Athens: UTC+3 → UTC+2\n• Europe/Sofia: UTC+3 → UTC+2\n• Europe/Bucharest: UTC+3 → UTC+2\n• Europe/Vilnius: UTC+3 → UTC+2\n• Europe/Riga: UTC+3 → UTC+2\n• Europe/Tallinn: UTC+3 → UTC+2\n• Europe/Helsinki: UTC+3 → UTC+2\n• Europe/Chisinau: UTC+3 → UTC+2\n• Europe/Kiev (Kyiv): UTC+3 → UTC+2\n• Asia/Nicosia: UTC+3 → UTC+2\n• Asia/Beirut: UTC+3 → UTC+2\n• Asia/Jerusalem (Tel Aviv\, Jerusalem): UTC+3 → UTC+2
END:VEVENT

BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:dst-2026-egypt-fall@mytimeanddate
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20261029
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20261030
